{"tid":2512371,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港台將刪除YouTube及FB上架逾一年片段","createTime":"2021-05-01T16:00:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T14:10:59.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"cf96e847683c488d6b9969a7d984e9c21121f3cd","tid":2512371,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T16:00:57.000Z","msg":"港台將刪除YouTube及FB上架逾一年片段<br />\n<br />\n香港電台發言人證實，港台將刪除於YouTube及Facebook等平台，上架超過一年的片段，至於有否具體執行有關措施的時間、哪些節目受影響，發言人說，暫時沒有補充。<br />\n<br />\n港台的YouTube及Facebook平台，目前不設閱覽期限。發言人解釋，有關新安排只是與港台官方網頁的一貫做法看齊，目前港台官網只提供過去12個月的節目重溫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588809-20210501.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588809-20210501.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=cd90c739\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588809-20210501.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=92b7f8ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588809-20210501.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"18bbec9d4792cbcde8afb117a292149c6b1c2e91","tid":2512371,"uid":345199,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T16:05:03.000Z","msg":"仆街李百全<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec3800df6f602da76acf065dc2cf8acd42c1bd82","tid":2512371,"uid":28202,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T16:09:20.000Z","msg":"back up<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35037da2295b6d414eb5671efed2091108599361","tid":2512371,"uid":27664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T16:09:26.000Z","msg":"相反緬甸抗爭者真正做實事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" c